  "description": "Proc is a triple voltage processor and summing amplifier module that provides continuous control over attenuation, inversion, and bias. It's a flexible tool in any modular video system that allows voltage control over signal mixing, conversion, and modulation. Proc offers essential functions for combining and transforming video signals and modulation sources. Learn more about Proc on our documentation website!"
